
1  “Pakuru Nyasacha kugoyo bul.

Adier, weruru ni Ruoth kugoyo gara.

Werneuru wende zaburi gi wende pak,

kumiyogo nyinge duong’.

Adier, luonguru nyinge maler.


2  Ruoth Nyasaye en Nyasaye makeyo lwenje nono.

Oseguro hembe e kind joge,

mondo oresa e lwet wasika.


3  “Jo-Asuria nobiro kalor e gode man yo nyandwat

Ne gibiro gi jolweny gana gi gana,

mi gipong’o holni duto.

Faresegi bende noimo gode.


4  Ne giramo ni nyaka giwang’ pinywa

mi gineg yawuotwa gi ligangla,

kendo gichwad nyithindwa mapod dhoth piny,

ka gimayowa nyithindwa matindo,

kendo gipeyo nyiwa.


5  To Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto

notamogi timo kamano

mana gi lwet dhako!


6  Ok yawuowi marateke

ema nonego thwon-gi marahuma!

Kata ok yawuot joma rabede

ema nogoye piny,

bende ok thuondi ma josunga

ema nomonje,

to ne en mana Judith nyar Merari

ema nolombe gi chia wang’e moloye!


7  Nolonyo lepe mag ywak,

mondo ojiw jogo mithiro e Israel.

Nowiro wang’e gi mo mang’ue ng’ar,


8  kendo noloso yie wiye,

mosidhoe ligisa,

eka norwakore gi law maber

mondo olombgo Holoferno.


9  Wuochene nomiyo chunye oridore,

kendo chia wang’e noketho parone

to ligangla nong’ado wiye oko!


10  Kane jo-Persia owinjo chir ma en-go

ne gitetni

kendo jo-Media bende nowuoro chiwruok mane ochiworego!


11  Kihondko nomako wasigu

kane giwinjo ka yawuotwa giyo,

kendo kane jowa moyomno

omedo giyo matek

to ne gidoko maluor

mi gitetni.

To kane jowago ogiyo matek moloyo,

ne giringo!


12  Yawuot mon ma jotich

nochwowogi mbure,

kahinyogi mana ka wasumbini

maringo buto.

Mano e kaka oganda lweny mar Ruoth Nyasacha

notiekogi.


13  “Abiro wero wer manyien ni Nyasacha.

A Ruoth Nyasaye,

in iduong’ moloyo.

In gi teko malich miwuoro,

kendo onge ng’ama nyalo loyi.


14  Ber mondo gik moko duto mane ichweyo, otini.

Nimar niwacho mana wach kende

mi gik moko duto obetie,

kendo nikudho muchi,

mi gibedo gi kido ma gin-go.

Onge ng’ama nyalo tamore

timo gima iwacho!


15  Gode yiengni

kendo nembe tugore e nymi;

lwendni bende koneni

to leny mana ka bor,

to pod isiko kibedo mang’won

ni jogo moluori.


16  Onge misango moro miwang’o madum mamit

manyalo miyi mor midwaro,

kendo kata mana boche duto mae piny

ok oromo timonigi misango miwang’o pep!

To ng’ama oluori,

in Ruoth Nyasaye,

ema nigi duong’’ mosiko.


17  Mano kaka ogendini mamonjo ogandawa none malit!

Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto

nokumgi chieng’ mong’adoe bura.

Enomi mach wang’ ringregi

kendo kudni chamgi

mi giniywag

kagiwinjo rem nyaka chieng’.”


18  Kane gichopo Jerusalem, ne gikulore piny mi gilamo Nyasaye, kendo kane gisepwodhore, ne gitimo misengni maggi miwang’o pep, kod misengni mane gitimo kuom herogi giwegi, kendo ne gikelo chiwo. 
19  To gik moko duto mag Holoferno mane jo-Israel osemiyo Judith, kaachiel gi net mane en owuon oyiecho e kitanda holoferno, nochiwo ni Nyasaye ka mich moyangone. 
20  Kuom dueche adek, ji nobedo mamor ka gitimo nyasi Jerusalem e nyim Hekalu, ka judith ni kodgi.

Judith otho ka hike oniang’


21  Kane ndalogo oserumo, ji duto nodok dala. Judith bende nodok Bethulia mi odak e dala chwore. Humbe nolak e piny ngima e ndalo duto mag ngimane. 
22  Ji mang’eny ne dwaro mondo okende, to chakre chieng’ mane Manase chwore othoe moyike but kwerene, ne ok oyie mondo ochak obed gi dichwo moro kendo. 
23  Humbe nomedo lak kendo nodak e dala chwore nyaka hike nochopo mia achiel gabich, mi nogonyo jatichne e tich misumba, moweye odhi thuolo. Achien notho Bethulia, mi oyike e liel mane oyikie Manase chwore, 
24  kendo jo-Israel noywage kuom ndalo abiriyo. Kane pok otho nopogo mwandune duto ni wede Manase chwore, kendo ni wedene owuon.


25  Onge ng’ama nochako ohedhore mondo othag jo-Israel e kinde duto mane Judith pod ngima, kata kuom ndalo mang’eny bang’ thone.

